Package: slice
Version: 0.1-1
Date: 2020-01-10
Title: Manipulating Activity Space Data for the Measurement of Segregation
Author: Seong-Yun Hong [aut, cre], Changlock Choi [ctb]
Maintainer: Seong-Yun Hong <syhong@khu.ac.kr>
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0), methods, stats, sp
Imports: splancs
Suggests: spdep, spgrass6, rgdal
Description: Measuring spatial segregation. The methods implemented in this 
        package include White's P index (1983) <doi:10.1086/227768>, 
        Morrill's D(adj) (1991), Wong's D(w) and D(s) (1993) 
        <doi:10.1080/00420989320080551>, and Reardon and O'Sullivan's set of 
        spatial segregation measures (2004) 
        <doi:10.1111/j.0081-1750.2004.00150.x>.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/syunhong/slice
NeedsCompilation: yes
Packaged: 2019-12-18 05:31:01 UTC; Seong-Yun
Repository: CRAN
Date/Publication: 2019-12-18 15:20:02 UTC
